  "description": "A long exposure night shot showcases a bridge spanning a body of water, likely a bay or strait. The bridge is illuminated with a series of orange lights along its length, creating a vibrant contrast against the dark blue-black of the water and night sky. The bridge\u2019s central tower is brightly lit in red and white, drawing the eye. The scene is framed by dark, silhouetted foliage in the foreground, adding depth and a natural element. Reflections of the lights shimmer on the water's surface. The overall impression is one of peacefulness and grandeur.",
